  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective randomised study is to investigate electrocardiographic
      alterations after intravascular injection of three different test solutions of bupivacaine
      and epinephrine in anaesthetised children up to 16 years of age.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
